# Web App Patterns

- Reuse `apps/web/components` and `packages/ui` primitives before new UI.
- API calls go through `apps/web/lib/api.ts` (auth header + 401 logout).
- State: existing Zustand stores and hooks in `store/*`, `hooks/*`.
- URLs: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` only — no hardcoded production domains.
- Layout: routes in `app/**`, UI in `components/**`, helpers in `lib/**`.
- Keep diffs focused; avoid unrelated page refactors.
- After user-flow changes → Playwright MCP smoke test on affected path.
